<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8135379>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Psyrassa spp.(A-F) P.tysoni sp. nov., holotype female:(A) Dorsal habitus;(B)Ventral habitus;(C) Lateral habitus; (D) Head,frontal view;(E) Head,lateral view; (F) Procoxal cavities. (G-J) P.pertenuis (Casey,1924), holotype: (G) Lateroventral view; (H) Dorsal habitus; (I) Head, frontal view;(J) Partial lateral habitus. Figures G,I, and J byEugenio H.Nearns;figure H from Lingafelter et al.(2023)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8135379/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

